                     <interp inst="t18260914-473-person2421" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
            . I took the prisoners on the 11th of July, in Aldersgate-street, near Adams' shop; we had been watching them; I saw Garroway cross the road - Bacon came to him with something under his coat - I seized him, and took him with the breeches; Birdseys ran and took Garroway.(Property produced and sworn to).</p>
               <p>BACON'S Defence. I bought them.</p>
